<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.4">
<l>maruntāku meṉṟaṅkōr māya valavaicoṟ koṇṭunīr</l>
<l>karuñcōṟu maṟṟaic ceñcōṟuṅ kaḷaṉiḻait teṉpaya</l>
<l>ṉoruṅkāka vēyula kēḻum viḻuṅki yumiḻntiṭṭa</l>
<l>peruntevaṉ pērcol lakiṟki livaḷaip peṟutirē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking thus the word of a deceitful woman that [that] be the remedy, your</l>
<l>preparing the [dance] floor with black rice [and] else with red rice, what [is] the use?</l>
<l>If you speak the name of the great god who swallowed down in one</l>
<l>all the seven worlds [and] spit them out again, you will get her [back].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
